OL,3,CWhy can the suspect in the Southport
OL,4,Cattack now be named?
OL,6,FA teenager charged with the murder of
OL,7,Fthree girls in the Southport stabbings
OL,8,Fhas now been named as Axel Rudakubana.
OL,10,FThe 17-year-old has also been charged
OL,11,Fwith the attempted murder of eight
OL,12,Fother children and two adults, as well
OL,13,Fas possession of a kitchen knife.
OL,15,FQuestions were raised after
OL,16,FRudakubana's arrest about why his
OL,17,Fidentity had not been made public
OL,18,Fwhile detectives were given more time
OL,19,Fto question him.
