OL,3,CWhy can the suspect in the Southport
OL,4,Cattack now be named?
OL,6,FAt Liverpool Crown Court on Thursday 1
OL,7,FAugust, Judge Andrew Menary KC ruled
OL,8,Fhe would not impose reporting
OL,9,Frestrictions to keep the defendant's
OL,10,Fidentity anonymous and said:
OL,11,F"Continuing to prevent the full
OL,12,Freporting has the disadvantage of
OL,13,Fallowing others to spread
OL,14,Fmisinformation, in a vacuum."
OL,16,FEarlier in the day, Rudakubana
OL,17,Fappeared at Liverpool Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt, which was sitting as a youth
OL,19,Fcourt, where automatic reporting
OL,20,Frestrictions were applied due to him
OL,21,Fbeing under the age of 18.
