OL,3,CWhy can the suspect in the Southport
OL,4,Cattack now be named?
OL,6,FThe boy was not identified earlier
OL,7,Fthis week because of his age amid
OL,8,Factive ongoing criminal proceedings.
OL,10,FThe criminal age of responsibility in
OL,11,FEngland and Wales is 10-years-old,
OL,12,Fmeaning children aged between 10 and
OL,13,F17 can be arrested and taken to court
OL,14,Fif they commit a crime.
