OL,3,CWhy can the suspect in the Southport
OL,4,Cattack now be named?
OL,6,FBut media organisations typically
OL,7,Frefrain from identifying any child
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of a crime,
OL,9,Fhaving considered their ethical and
OL,10,Fother legal responsibilities, because
OL,11,Fthere is the prospect this could then
OL,12,Flead to prosecution and court
OL,13,Fproceedings where the reporting
OL,14,Frestrictions in question will activate.
