OL,3,CWhy can the suspect in the Southport
OL,4,Cattack now be named?
OL,6,FIn February, teenagers Scarlett
OL,7,FJenkinson and Eddie Ratcliffe were
OL,8,Fidentified for the first time as they
OL,9,Fwere both handed life sentences for
OL,10,Fthe murder of transgender 16-year-old
OL,11,FBrianna Ghey in February 2023, after a
OL,12,Fjudge lifted a ban on them being named
OL,13,Fby the press.
OL,15,FBut the restrictions automatically end
OL,16,Fwhen the child turns 18.
