OL,3,CWhy can the suspect in the Southport
OL,4,Cattack now be named?
OL,6,FIn Rudakubana's crown court hearing,
OL,7,Fin light of applications by lawyers to
OL,8,Fimpose a section 45 restriction, Judge
OL,9,FAndrew Menary said: "Whilst I accept
OL,10,Fit is exceptional, given his age,
OL,11,Fprincipally because he is 18 in six
OL,12,Fdays' time, I do not make an order
OL,13,Funder section 45".
